    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>你有没有想过，成为一枚洲际弹道导弹会是什么感觉？</i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>BRAINSHELL 是一款专注于沉浸感与叙事的心理恐怖体验。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206220/extras/1ea2d7ee02b5a9e8e747d1099374bb2a.avif?t=1770537700\" width=852 height=192 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏将把你带进一个故事，这个故事扭曲了脆弱的人类心智，充满了恐怖的宣传和洗脑。</strong> 当你踏上第一次、也是最后一次任务时，残酷训练的记忆浮现。你将在疯狂的边缘摇摆，操控人类的末日，并一步步坠入超现实的幻觉之中。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >忽视幻觉</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206220/extras/f736d1683c44a1c4f9ed546d9c8412cd.poster.avif?t=1770537700\" width=852 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206220/extras/f736d1683c44a1c4f9ed546d9c8412cd.webm?t=1770537700\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206220/extras/f736d1683c44a1c4f9ed546d9c8412cd.mp4?t=1770537700\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将操作冷战时期风格的控制面板，引到这头人类制造的怪物，并拼凑出一个扭曲世界历史，在这里，计算机被人脑取代。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >记住训练</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206220/extras/cdc7b1f87e2537d4b85663f5cd94eb0f.poster.avif?t=1770537700\" width=852 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206220/extras/cdc7b1f87e2537d4b85663f5cd94eb0f.webm?t=1770537700\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206220/extras/cdc7b1f87e2537d4b85663f5cd94eb0f.mp4?t=1770537700\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >结局是不可避免的。你无法逃脱困住你的金属外壳。你就是武器，而武器必须被使用。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >你是我们国家的希望</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206220/extras/20b7f58192b59e6a574cddeea932a7a7.poster.avif?t=1770537700\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206220/extras/20b7f58192b59e6a574cddeea932a7a7.webm?t=1770537700\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206220/extras/20b7f58192b59e6a574cddeea932a7a7.mp4?t=1770537700\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
